user story  :As the Concept Coding / NER service,
I want to refine and validate the topic modeling logic using UMLS data,
so that extracted intents and entities are more accurate, relevant, and aligned with real clinical content before production deployment.

This story focuses on improving model quality by testing against a coding system(s) in UMLS, tuning extraction logic, adjusting filtering thresholds, and validating semantic outputs. The goal is to move from theoretical or synthetic assumptions to data-driven refinement, improving precision, recall, and overall semantic relevance.

